            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="chatMainContainer" class="chat-maincontainer d-none">
            <div id="chatSection" class="chat-section rounded-1">
                <div class="chat-header fii-content-title clearfix">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-lg-6">
                            <div id="chatHeaderRecipient" class="chat-about ">
                                <h5 class="fw-bold">Aiden Chavez</h5>
                                <small id="">Last seen: 2 hours ago</small>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-6 hidden-sm text-right">
                            <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="btn btn-outline-warning"><i class="fa fa-paperclip"></i></a>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div id="chatHistory" class="chat-history">
                    <ul id="chatHistoryContent" class="m-b-0">
                        <li class="clearfix">
                            <div class="message-data ">
                                <span class="message-data-time">10:10 AM, Today</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="message other-message "> Hi Aiden, how are you? How is the project coming along? </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="clearfix">
                            <div class="message-data text-right">
                                <span class="message-data-time">10:12 AM, Today</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="message my-message float-right">Are we meeting today?</div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="clearfix">
                            <div class="message-data text-right">
                                <span class="message-data-time">10:15 AM, Today</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="message my-message float-right">Project has been already finished and I have results to show you.</div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="clearfix">
                            <div class="message-data ">
                                <span class="message-data-time">10:10 AM, Today</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="message other-message ">
                                Hi Aiden, how are you? How is the project coming along?
                                Hi Aiden, how are you? How is the project coming along?
                                Hi Aiden, how are you? How is the project coming along?
                                Hi Aiden, how are you? How is the project coming along?
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="fii-form chat-message clearfix">
                    <div class="input-group mb-0 justify-content-center">
                        <div class="input-group-prepend">
                            <span class="input-group-text"><i class="fa fa-paper-plane"></i></span>
                        </div>
                        <textarea id="messageContent" class="form-control " placeholder="Your messages..." messageType="text"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="recipientSection" class="recipient-section fii-form rounded-1">
                <div class="input-group mb-1">
                    <div class="input-group-prepend">
                        <span class="input-group-text"><i class="fa fa-search"></i></span>
                    </div>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Search...">
                </div>
                <!-- begin::List Invidual Recipient -->
                <div class="fii-content-title position-sticky">
                    <i class="fas fa-user"></i>
                    <span class="custom-header">INVIDUAL</span>
                </div>
                <ul id="listSingleRecipient" class=" list-unstyled chat-list mt-2 mb-0">
                    <li class="clearfix">
                        <div class="about">
                            <div class="name">Vincent Porter</div>
                            <div class="status"> <i class="fa fa-circle offline"></i> left 7 mins ago </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="clearfix active">
